videos.description: Riley Ferguson finds an open Darrell Henderson for a 17-yard touchdown to give the Tigers an early lead.
videos.headline: Tigers score first with TD

videos.description: Luke Skipper rushes 10 yards for Tulsa's first touchdown of the night to chip away at Memphis' lead.
videos.headline: Skipper rushes into to the end zone for TD

videos.description: Tony Pollard breaks several tackles and rushes for 59 yards to the end zone for the touchdown.
videos.headline: Pollard streaks for a 59-yard TD

videos.description: Chad President finds a gap and rushes seven yards to the end zone for a touchdown to tie Memphis.
videos.headline: Tulsa ties it with rushing TD

videos.description: Riley Ferguson passes it to an open Anthony Miller who makes a diving catch for the touchdown.
videos.headline: Miller makes diving TD catch

videos.description: Memphis coach Mike Norvell breaks down what the Tigers need to improve on in the second half.
videos.headline: Norvell: 'We got to get cleaned up'

videos.description: Patrick Taylor Jr. pushes his way into the end zone for a 1-yard touchdown to pad Memphis' lead.
videos.headline: Taylor muscles his way into the end zone

videos.description: Riley Ferguson finds an open Damonte Coxie for a 9-yard touchdown to make the score 38-14.
videos.headline: Memphis pads lead with Ferguson's fourth passing TD

videos.description: Riley Ferguson led his team with four passing touchdowns and Anthony Miller shined in the Tigers' win over the Golden Hurricane.
videos.headline: Offense leads the way in Memphis' victory over Tulsa
